note right of AppConnector
Facade of the application layer.
UI should enter here,
not into domain.
end note

note bottom of DomainContracts
Domain stays pure:
no dependency on UI
or Application.
end note

note bottom of MenuTemplateCatalog
Seed modules represented here:
menu-template-weightloss-2b.js
menu-template-standard-1a.js
menu-template-gain-1a.js
menu-template-monday-weightloss.js
...
